rows.label: qst702803_msg0001
rows.name:
Strange, there seems
to be nothing inside.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0002
rows.name: ...Which means...

rows.label: qst702803_msg0003
rows.name: So it's come to this.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0004
rows.name: It's too late to notice now, mo.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0005
rows.name:
You're the chairman of
the Chamber of Commerce!

rows.label: qst702803_msg0006
rows.name:
So you're the ones who've been
ruining my precious merchandise, mo?

rows.label: qst702803_msg0007
rows.name: ...A pity, mo.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0008
rows.name: Funny, I feel the same way.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0009
rows.name:
Why were you leaving that "precious
merchandise" all over the place? Why
not conduct business in a shop?

rows.label: qst702803_msg0010
rows.name:
It's because you have
something to hide.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0011
rows.name: Let's not jump to conclusions.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0012
rows.name:
...If you have a reason,
I'll hear it, Morumo.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0013
rows.name: Mo mo! Morumo is not in the wrong, mo!

rows.label: qst702803_msg0014
rows.name:
Dangerous things have value,
mo. And where there's value,
there's business, mo.

rows.label: qst702803_msg0015
rows.name:
What's wrong with a merchant
doing business, mo?!

rows.label: qst702803_msg0016
rows.name:
So it's okay to do anything
as long as it makes money?

rows.label: qst702803_msg0017
rows.name:
You can't chase a dream
without money, mo. This is
no time for pretty words, mo!

rows.label: qst702803_msg0018
rows.name:
Of all things to say, "a
dream". Who's the one
spewing pretty words now?

rows.label: qst702803_msg0019
rows.name:
Be quiet, mo! I don't want
to hear your lectures, mo!

rows.label: qst702803_msg0020
rows.name:
I quite liked you all, mo. But if you're
going to get in Morumo's way, I have no
choice but to make you disappear, mo!
